Seems they said my full name again, they are getting clearer too.   This 
was with Frank's Box #27 today.  Frank mentioned noisy boxes, so i did  a 
short session with this radio.  This is an original and untouched piece  of 
audio available to anybody that wants it to validate the file.  
 
The thing is, the box works and backing it up with proof of your own  name 
that is not common to hear on the radio should make skeptics think again  
before they bash what we do.
 
-Steve Hultay
